headline.main: China to Keep Prices Stable This Year, Deepen Reforms: State Planner
headline.print_headline: China to Keep Prices Stable This Year, Deepen Reforms: State Planner

lead_paragraph: China will ensure prices stay basically stable this year while at the same time deepening price reform, a vice chairman at the state planner said on Monday.
